low-prevention.html\">Annual Inspections</a><a href=\"backflow-prevention.html\">Backflow Prevention</a><a href=\"commercial-emergency.html\">24/7 Commercial Emergency</a></div>\n            <div class=\"mega-cta\">\n              <h2>Commercial Service</h2>\n              <p>Restaurants, retail, condos and property managers. Same-day response across the GTA.</p>\n              <a class=\"button\" href=\"tel:+16479809211\">647-980-9211</a>\n              <small>Get a free assessment</small>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a  href=\"blog.html\">Blog</a>\n        <a  href=\"about.html\">About</a>\n        <a  href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n      </nav>\n      <a class=\"call-link\" href=\"tel:+16479809211\">Call 647-980-9211</a>\n    </header>\n  \n    <main class=\"page-hero\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Commercial service</p>\n        <h1>Commercial plumbing and electrical service in Brampton</h1>\n        <p>Fateh Plumbing & Electric supports restaurants, retail units, offices, condos, industrial spaces, property managers, and local businesses with commercial plumbing and electrical service from Brampton across the GTA.</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"button\" href=\"tel:+16479809211\">Call 647-980-9211</a>\n          <a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"contact.html\">Request assessment</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <img class=\"page-hero-photo\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556911220-bff31c812dba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80\" alt=\"Commercial kitchen service consultation for plumbing and electrical work\" width=\"700\" height=\"460\">\n    </main>\n    <section class=\"band commercial-columns\">\n      \n        <article class=\"service-card\">\n          <h2>Restaurant & Food Service</h2>\n          <ul class=\"check-list\"><li>Restaurant Plumbing</li><li>Commercial Kitchen Plumbing</li><li>Grease Trap Cleaning</li><li>Grease Trap Installation</li></ul