"false\">\n        <rect x=\"4\" y=\"7\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" rx=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M16 11l4-2v6l-4-2\"></path>\n      </svg>\n    </span><strong>Inspections & Diagnostics</strong></span><span>Sewage Line Inspection, Video Camera Inspection, Industrial Plumbing</span></a><a href=\"commercial.html\"><span class=\"link-card-head\">\n    <span class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" focusable=\"false\">\n        <path d=\"M12 3l7 3v5c0 5-3.1 8.8-7 10-3.9-1.2-7-5-7-10V6l7-3z\"></path><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"></path>\n      </svg>\n    </span><strong>Compliance & Safety</strong></span><span>Annual Inspections, Backflow Prevention, 24/7 Commercial Emergency</span></a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  \n    <section class=\"band faq\">\n      <div class=\"section-heading\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">Commercial FAQ</p>\n        <h2>Common questions about commercial plumbing and electrical in Brampton</h2>\n      </div>\n      <details><summary>Do you provide commercial plumbing and electrical in Brampton?</summary><p>Fateh Plumbing & Electric provides commercial plumbing and electrical in Brampton and related plumbing services across Greater Toronto Area. Call to describe the issue, confirm availability, and choose the next step.</p></details><details><summary>Can I get same-day plumbing service?</summary><p>Same-day service depends on schedule, location, and the urgency of the problem. Active leaks, sewer backups, and no-water situations are treated as priority calls.</p></details><details><summary>How do I know if I need a plumber right away?</summary><p>Call right away for active leaks, standing water, sewage backup, burst pipes, no hot water in essential situations, or a fixture that cannot be shut off safely.</p></details><details><summary>Do you handle both small repairs and larger plumbing jobs?</summary><p>Fateh Plumbing & Electric handles small repairs such as toilets an